97 contract separately with such a provider for such coverage, provided that such coverage
98 is paid for entirely using only funds not authorized or appropriated by the state."
99 SECTION 5.
100 This Act shall become effective upon its approval by the Governor or upon its becoming law
101 without such approval.
102 SECTION 6.
103 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
